OL,3,CJury deliberations begin in trial over
OL,4,Cdeath of grandad in alleged hit and run
OL,6,FA jury has begun its deliberations in
OL,7,Fthe trial of a father and son accused
OL,8,Fof murdering a grandfather by driving
OL,9,Fa van into a group of people.
OL,11,FBrian Darby, 60, was carried 150m on
OL,12,Fthe bonnet of Martin Breeze's Citroen
OL,13,FBerlingo when it left the road and
OL,14,Fdrove over a grass verge, onto a
OL,15,Ffootpath in Ingleby Barwick, Teesside,
OL,16,Fat around 11.30pm on 2 February.
