OL,3,CJury deliberations begin in trial over
OL,4,Cdeath of grandad in alleged hit and run
OL,6,FTeesside Crown Court heard that Shaun
OL,7,FBreeze had rung his father after he
OL,8,Fgot into a disagreement with a group
OL,9,Fof people who had enjoyed a night out
OL,10,Fat a local bar.
OL,12,FThe prosecution claimed the father and
OL,13,Fson were out for "revenge" that night
OL,14,Fwhen Martin Breeze drove into the
OL,15,Fgroup, killing Mr Darby, injuring
OL,16,Fthree other people and narrowly
OL,17,Fmissing a fifth.
OL,19,FThe Crown claimed Martin Breeze had
OL,20,Fbeen encouraged by his son.
