OL,3,CJury deliberations begin in trial over
OL,4,Cdeath of grandad in alleged hit and run
OL,6,FPainter and decorator Martin Breeze,
OL,7,F56, of Irthing Close, Ingleby Barwick,
OL,8,Fhas admitted causing death by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving and causing serious
OL,10,Finjury by dangerous driving but denies
OL,11,Fmurder, attempted murder and
OL,12,Fperverting the course of justice by
OL,13,Flater claiming the van had been stolen.
OL,15,FShaun Breeze, 28, of Owls Grove,
OL,16,FIngleby Barwick, denies the same
OL,17,Fcharges, saying he was not in charge
OL,18,Fof the van.
